基础设施建设等领域的双边合作。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 11:48:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-xi-underscores-benefits-cooperation-with-slovakia-during-ficos-visit-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>亚马逊安抚情绪，工资到期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-11-01/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 10:17:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>官员称，中国希望美国无论谁赢得大选，都将继续在气候变化问题上合作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/china-hopes-us-will-continue-climate-change-collaboration-whoever-wins-election-2024-11-01/</link><description>一位政府高级官员周五表示，无论下周总统选举结果如何，中国希望美国能够继续在气候变化问题上与其他国家合作。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 10:16:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/china-hopes-us-will-continue-climate-change-collaboration-whoever-wins-election-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>受制裁打击的中国科技行业对特朗普和哈里斯总统任期的影响感到困惑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-sanction-hit-tech-industry-puzzles-over-impact-trump-harris-presidencies-2024-11-01/</link><description>唐纳德·特朗普下周赢得美国总统职位将比卡马拉·哈里斯获胜更让中国科技公司的前景变得混乱，高管们表示，他不可预测的风格可能会导致受到制裁打击的行业得到缓和，就像增加限制一样。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 08:10:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-sanction-hit-tech-industry-puzzles-over-impact-trump-harris-presidencies-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲黄金庆祝活动引发印度购买热潮，但成交量滞后</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/asia-gold-festivities-trigger-buying-spree-india-volumes-lag-2024-11-01/</link><description>印度的黄金需求本周因节日采购而猛增，但由于价格创历史新高，成交量低于平时。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 07:14:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/asia-gold-festivities-trigger-buying-spree-india-volumes-lag-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>早间竞价：值得纪念的十一月......</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-11-01/</link><description>Stella Qiu 展望欧洲和全球市场未来一天</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 05:33:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>中国转向美国农产品进口有助于抵御贸易战风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-pivot-us-farm-imports-bolsters-it-against-trade-war-risks-2024-11-01/</link><description>中国自2018年以来努力改变粮食进口来源，这使得如果美国总统大选后中美贸易摩擦爆发，中国更有能力对美国农产品征收针锋相对的关税，同时减少对中国粮食安全的损害。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 04:29:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-pivot-us-farm-imports-bolsters-it-against-trade-war-risks-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲工厂活动停滞不前，削弱了中国的反弹势头</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-economy-asias-factory-activity-stagnates-taking-shine-off-rebound-china-2024-11-01/</link><description>对于预计美中贸易紧张局势加剧的政策制定者来说，这是令人沮丧的迹象。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 03:43:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-economy-asias-factory-activity-stagnates-taking-shine-off-rebound-china-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>美国谴责对中国著名人权捍卫者的判刑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-condemns-sentencing-prominent-chinese-human-rights-defenders-2024-11-01/</link><description>美国周五谴责中国著名人权律师余文生及其妻子徐艳的“不公正监禁”，中国一家法院本周分别判处他们三年和一年零九个月的刑期。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 03:20:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-condemns-sentencing-prominent-chinese-human-rights-defenders-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国研究人员在梅塔骆驼背上开发军事用途人工智能模型</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/chinese-researchers-develop-ai-model-military-use-back-metas-llama-2024-11-01/</link><description>根据三篇学术论文和分析师的说法，与中国人民解放军有联系的中国顶级研究机构已使用 Meta 公开的 Llama 模型来开发一种用于潜在军事应用的人工智能工具。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 02:38:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/chinese-researchers-develop-ai-model-military-use-back-metas-llama-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>台风“康瑞”残骸掠过中国海岸后，台湾进行了清理工作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/taiwan-clears-up-remnant-typhoon-kong-rey-brushes-chinese-coast-2024-11-01/</link><description>周五，强大的台风“康瑞”席卷台湾，造成两人死亡，交通运输中断，风暴余波掠过中国海岸后，台湾天气晴朗，办公楼和金融市场重新开放。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 02:35:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/taiwan-clears-up-remnant-typhoon-kong-rey-brushes-chinese-coast-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>对 10 月份非农就业数据反应平淡后，收益率下跌，股价上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-11-01/</link><description>数据显示美国经济 10 月份几乎没有增加任何就业机会，但周五美国政府债券收益率下跌，股票期货小幅上涨，尽管这些数据受到工业行动和飓风的严重干扰。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 02:12:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-11-01/</guid></item></channel></rss>